text: The Annecy Round was a multi-year multilateral trade negotiation (MTN) between 26 nation-states that were parties to the GATT. This second round took place in 1949 in Annecy, France. 13 countries took part in the round. The main focus of the talks was more tariff reductions, around 5,000 in total. ==References== Category:World Trade Organization Category:General Agreement on Tariffs and Trade Category:Commercial treaties Category:Treaties concluded in 1949
title: Annecy Round
